 Tom McTevia , 42 , who was left without the use of his legs following another ATV accident 11 years ago , was traveling with a group and driving his friend Tina Hoisington , 45 , near an overlook at Lake Pend Oreille in Bonner County on Sunday .
When the group stopped for a photograph around noon , he 's ATV got too close to the edge of the 2,100-foot cliff and went over .
